title: The Parrots "D D Dangerous" : Converse Red Light Sessions
description:
Converse Make Noise winners "The Parrots" flew in to Amsterdam to record at our first European Rubber Tracks pop-up studio. While in town, they also found time to drop in to Red Light Radio and record this loud session for us too.

Track: "D D Dangerous"
